This is the help file for the securecopymagnus program

The program uses scp to coppy files.
Please change paths for personal use.
This program is maintained by Michael under a GNU General Public Licence; email 19319740@student.curtin.edu.au

use
	securecopymagnus [drive] path/in/drive.txt [directory]

where "drive" may be 	"-s" for scratch or
			"-g" for group or
			"-h" for help
and "directory" may be blank



EOF
